        {
          "id": "EFVANTW1gYtYgU2La7s8",
          "description": "🌟 I'm excited to introduce a phonics program that turns letter sounds into reading superpowers! This isn’t just about memorizing sounds—it’s about discovering the magic of reading through fun, organized learning that kids love.\n\nHere’s what makes this course special:\n\n✨ Step-by-Step Success\nStarting with simple sounds (like /a/ and /m/) and building to advanced words (like \"splash\" and \"bright\"), we move at the perfect speed to build confidence and skill.\n\n🚀 Learning That Feels Like Play\nWho says phonics has to be boring? Through games, songs, and hands-on activities, we make every sound easy to remember and every word a fun discovery!\n\n📚 Real Reading from Day One\nYour child won’t just practice sounds—they’ll use them right away in fun decodable books, feeling the joy of real reading from the very start.\n\n🎯 Skills That Last\nBy mixing phonics with sight words and understanding, we create readers who don’t just sound out words but truly enjoy and understand what they read.\n\nPerfect for:\n• Preschoolers starting their reading journey\n• Young students mastering the basics\n• Older students who need more confidence\n\nReady to watch your child’s reading skills grow fast? Let’s begin the phonics adventure! 🚀",
          "discount60min": 0,
          "duration": 30,
          "hourlyRate": 35.2,
